sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Customer
    participant Web as Web Frontend
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Payment as Payment Service
    participant Shipping as Shipping Service
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant DB as Database

    Note over Customer,DB: E-Commerce Order Processing Flow

    Customer->>Web: Browse products
    Web->>API: GET /products
    API->>Inventory: Check stock levels
    Inventory->>DB: Query inventory
    DB-->>Inventory: Stock data
    Inventory-->>API: Available products
    API-->>Web: Product catalog
    Web-->>Customer: Display products

    Customer->>Web: Add to cart
    Web->>Web: Store cart locally

    Customer->>Web: Proceed to checkout
    Web->>API: POST /checkout
    API->>Order: Create order draft
    Order->>DB: Insert order (PENDING)
    DB-->>Order: order_id

    API->>Inventory: Reserve items
    Inventory->>DB: Lock stock
    alt Stock Available
        DB-->>Inventory: Reserved
        Inventory-->>API: Success
    else Out of Stock
        DB-->>Inventory: Insufficient stock
        Inventory-->>API: Failure
        API-->>Web: Out of stock error
        Web-->>Customer: Show error
    end

    API->>Payment: Process payment
    Payment->>Payment: Validate card
    alt Payment Successful
        Payment->>DB: Store transaction
        Payment-->>API: Payment confirmed
        API->>Order: Update status (PAID)
        Order->>DB: Update order

        API->>Inventory: Confirm reservation
        Inventory->>DB: Decrement stock

        API->>Shipping: Create shipment
        Shipping->>DB: Insert shipping record
        Shipping->>Shipping: Calculate delivery date
        Shipping-->>API: Tracking number

        API->>Email: Send confirmation
        Email->>Customer: Order confirmation email

        API-->>Web: Order success
        Web-->>Customer: Show confirmation page

    else Payment Failed
        Payment-->>API: Payment declined
        API->>Order: Update status (FAILED)
        Order->>DB: Update order
        API->>Inventory: Release reservation
        Inventory->>DB: Unlock stock
        API-->>Web: Payment error
        Web-->>Customer: Show payment error
    end

    Note over Shipping: Background Process
    loop Every 2 hours
        Shipping->>DB: Query ready shipments
        Shipping->>Shipping: Generate labels
        Shipping->>Email: Send tracking updates
        Email->>Customer: Shipping notification
    end

    Customer->>Web: Track order
    Web->>API: GET /orders/:id
    API->>Order: Fetch order details
    Order->>DB: Query order
    API->>Shipping: Get tracking info
    Shipping->>DB: Query shipment
    DB-->>Shipping: Tracking events
    Shipping-->>API: Tracking data
    API-->>Web: Order status
    Web-->>Customer: Display tracking

    Note over Customer,DB: Order delivered
    Shipping->>DB: Update status (DELIVERED)
    Shipping->>Email: Delivery confirmation
    Email->>Customer: Thank you email

    Customer->>Web: Leave review
    Web->>API: POST /reviews
    API->>DB: Insert review
    API-->>Web: Review saved
    Web-->>Customer: Thank you message
